### 注册
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "demo_user",
  "password": "12345678",
  "email": "demo@example.com",
  "displayName": "Demo User"
}

### 登录
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "account": "demo_user",
  "password": "12345678"
}

### 当前用户
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 查询词书
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books?bookType=WORD
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 创建用户上传书籍元数据（正文保存在客户端）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "我的本地词书",
  "bookType": "WORD",
  "language": "en",
  "level": "BEGINNER",
  "itemCount": 120,
  "clientContentRef": "client://books/local-book-001",
  "contentHash": "local-content-hash"
}

### 查询词书单词
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/books/1/words
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 获取或创建当前单词计划
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/word-learning/plans/current
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 创建单词计划
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/word-learning/plans
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": 1,
  "dailyNewCount": 10,
  "dailyReviewCount": 20
}

### 获取今日新学/复习单词
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/word-learning/due-words
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 提交单词学习事件
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/word-learning/events
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "planId": 1,
  "wordId": 1,
  "activityType": "NEW",
  "selectedAnswer": "苹果",
  "correct": true,
  "durationMs": 3000,
  "clientEventId": "demo-event-001"
}

### 今日学习汇总
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/word-learning/summary/today
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 获取题目（替换 {{token}}）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/quiz/next
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 提交答案（替换 {{token}} 和 wordId）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/quiz/submit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "wordId": 1,
  "selectedAnswer": "苹果"
}

### 排行榜
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/ranking/top?limit=10
